meanings.definition: The number that is one more than eighteen and one less than twenty.
meanings.sent1: I counted to nineteen before stopping.
meanings.sent2: There are nineteen students in our class.
meanings.sent3: Nineteen cupcakes were left, but I ate them all!
meanings.sent4: Her age felt like a never-ending nineteen.
meanings.sent5: The clock struck nineteen times, signaling midnight.

meanings.definition: A group or set of nineteen people or things.
meanings.sent1: We formed a team of nineteen players for the game.
meanings.sent2: There were nineteen books on the shelf.
meanings.sent3: Nineteen puppies ran around the yard, causing chaos.
meanings.sent4: The room was filled with nineteen colorful balloons.
meanings.sent5: The garden had exactly nineteen roses in full bloom.
